                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, R</hi> 264). On 11th February, the prisoner was given into my custody by the last witness between 2 and 3 o'clock—I told him he was given into my custody for stealing a pair of boots—he said, "I know I have"—these are the boots—I did not see them on the prisoner—the boy had them.</p>
